         <abstract id="aspace_be11fc865bef6703db05565537cfc2f0">Photographs created by Marion Belanger, 2006-2012 and printed 2015 that document tectonic shifting of the North American Plate in California and Iceland. </abstract>
         <langmaterial id="aspace_caeea6547ee51f1ac595a51759cdc235">
            <language>Title page and inscriptions in English.</language>
         </langmaterial>
    
