            <scopecontent id="aspace_c899981816d4e44abdc7294f4be13f45">
               <head>Scope and Contents</head>
               <p>Views of sites along edges of the North American Plate including the Mid-Atlantic Rift in Iceland and San Andreas Fault in California created in 2006 and printed in 2015-2016 as ink jet prints, 12.875 x 16.375 inches (32.7 x 41.6 centimeters). The prints comprise an edition numbered one of five. Ancillary material includes a box with a mounted inkjet print, a signed title page, and interleaving paper.</p>
            </scopecontent>
